2014 Ballon d'Or winner Ronaldo pulls out a moonwalk whilst fully suited and booted 

It goes without saying that we have all grown to love his twinkletoed genius on the turf, but this advert may take some getting used to.

Having recently split from long-term girlfriend Irina Shayk, there's no knowing what sort of damage the 2014 Ballon d'Or winner will cause on the dance floor with moves like these.

However, it hasn't been plain sailing all the way for Ronaldo's big launch after sponsors Nike, who pay him around £5.5m a year, recently forced their client to withdraw a line of trainers from his new collection in the belief that it competed directly with one of their own.

